source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
<dl>
<dt><code>-a</code></dt>
<dd>
<p>Output all.</p>
</dd>
<dt><code>-b, --brief</code></dt>
<dd>
<p>Be brief about it.</p>
</dd>
<dt><code>--verbose</code></dt>
<dd>
<p>Talk a great deal.</p>
</dd>
<dt><code>-f FILE</code></dt>
<dd>
<p>Read input from FILE.</p>
</dd>
</dl>
<p>The description may also start on the next line:</p>
<dl>
<dt><code>--output=FILE</code></dt>
<dd>
<p>Write output to FILE instead of standard output.</p>
</dd>
</dl>
